here is a script that a few line of code 
that allows you to control the waves of water 
it is really basic


to change the density of the waves just change the value of the line

'Citizen.InvokeNative(0xC54A08C85AE4D410, 0.0)'

0.0 is the base value I advise you not to go beyond 1.0
the waves will be in the shape of a pick I tested the value 
to see if there would be any crashes but none even with a value of + 50.0






